Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The Council is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well of course they'd be angry after \Nwe keep running amuck all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master has been called before the Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:13.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:41.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Makarov, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are in the middle of the trial... I \Npresume you are not sleeping, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Lord has been disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jose has been stripped of his \Nplace among the 10 Wizard Saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, that's as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:37.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But to judge Fairy Tail \Nas completely "innocent?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have expected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful, Macky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I argued on your behalf, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt, Yaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the guild's fixed up, \Ncome over for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:56.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a Fairy Ramen with 12 pork slices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,12 slices is a bit much, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:04.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember you violated the ban on \Ninter-guild conflict in Paragraph 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put in 20 or 30 slices if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,12 pork slices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:19.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macky... Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're no longer young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't forgotten, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Rob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:33.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rob... Rob, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and you and Poluchka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rob too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We overdid it, but every day sure was a fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Rob quit Fairy Tail... Erza \Ntells me stories once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately many people are of the opinion that \NFairy Tail has gone too far too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Michello and Org have \Nrequested you be disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate you will be facing \Nserious punishment, Macky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead, you're no good to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Rob...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macky, hurry up and retire. \NFor the sake of your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:32.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! You can all take\Njobs again starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a temporary counter, \Nbut do all the jobs you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually they're just hanging \Naround not taking any jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I haven't seen Loke around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:05:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've finally fallen for \NLoke's magic touch then, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard that he found my \Nkeys, so I wanted to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll tell him if I see him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, weren't your Spirits angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About you dropping your keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it wasn't anything enough for \Nthem to get that mad about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to drop it, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remembering makes my butt sting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I chill it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need innuendo-style sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, let me see your bright red butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And no overt sexual harassment either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she'll look like \Nif I make it sting even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're just the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll tell you straight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need weaklings in this guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting humiliated by Phantom like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, I don't even know your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you there, the main culprit, the debutant \NCelestial Spirit user... It was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:17.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has been talking \Nabout who to blame for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say anything \Nwhen you didn't even help us fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:25.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the master says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah! It had nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although if I had been there, you \Nwouldn't have had all that trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus! Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heartless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fight would it be \Nwhen you can't even catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I inherit the guild, I'll \Nget rid of all the weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as anyone who stands against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the ultimate guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest guild in history \Nthat no one can look down upon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherit? What nonsense is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus is the master's grandson, you see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:28.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So when Master retires, the chances that \NLaxus becomes the next master are quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be against someone becoming the master \Nwho thinks that way about his allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor is that's why he \Nhasn't been able to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. You'll just tire \Nyourself out dealing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what do you think? Want to go do a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Gray and Lucy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a sense that we've been together \Never since the Eisenwald incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} you get a "sense" like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all thought it was pretty obvious. {not literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She never stopped to think about it herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Erza for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's form a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the four of us. Or \Nfive, if you count Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:27.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really want someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone that {\i1}is{\i0} you, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, things just \Nwouldn't fit right, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Fairy Tail's strongest \Nteam is official now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, Lucy's the strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was up against Aquarius, \NI couldn't win either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And her straight-man act is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The "strongest" in a lot of different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-With {\i1}him{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and do a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take down the Magic Sect operating in \Nthe shadows of the castle town of Lupinus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild's being remade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then the master should also \Npass to the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His attitude has some big problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's basically a poster-boy \Nfor lack of communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's Erza, but \Nshe's still too young... {Again, they didn't discuss Gildarts}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master? You're up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they've gone and done it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Erza and her team \Ndestroyed half a city while on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Council has requested you submit \Na written explanation immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Master, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:05.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retire? No frickin' way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You don't seem so well, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The job at Lupinus from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:18.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Natsu spewed fire everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray froze everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza especially!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy... You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, with all the destruction, most \Nof our reward goes to pay reparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won't be able \Nto pay this month's rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't I recommend \Na perfect job for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right up your alley, Lucy, and there's \Nno need to worry about destroying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onibas?  The city from the lullaby incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a request for us to use our magic to \Nattract lots of people to see a play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu can shoot fire, and you two can put on a show\Nwith your Creation Magic and her Requipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll move everyone's \Nhearts with Lyra's singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a wonderful \Nperformance, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever finish my novel, I \Nhope it gets turned into a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! This is a great opportunity \Nto study staging a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the people from Fairy Tail, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for accepting my request!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Just leave the stage work to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bit of a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The actors have all run out on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My plays have been more and more unpopular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, the actors are ashamed \Nto be in my productions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:21.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my wife tired of me \Nchasing my dream and left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get this "thanking" thing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:32.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the play is canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was something, but this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need actors, then \Nyou've got some right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing vocal exercises!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that does sound kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let your dream end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, might as well let them give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} you don't thank us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have one week until opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Fredrick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have come to save the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Erza! You've got quite the stage presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really gotten into the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, when we weren't practicing, we were \Nhanding out fliers and constructing the set...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remembering all the lines was pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:43.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, we were all in the spirit \Nof it and having more fun than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some fans are here to see \Nyou, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for the debut \Nperformance. Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've seen a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the invitation, Macky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see! How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to heckle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing \Nhere, fake Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Micheal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After my heart was hit with your fiery fist, \NI've given up forcibly scouting for pin-up girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that what happened again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:25.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy was thinking of naughty things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame, I'll be rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about having you come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you from Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again for back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And aren't you from Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also captivated by his power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's raw, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't make it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsundere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for that red dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's blue. And a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long until you destroy the moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I even need to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat, and the performance \Nhasn't even started...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally opening day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had such a large audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:33.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I never sang in front of so many people! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to put on a good show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Far, far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A story of long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:16:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A Prince of the West Kingdom fell in love \Nwith a Princess of a rival Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:01.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Prince is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:29.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}To save the Princess, the Prince of the West \NKingdom went to the mountain of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's one that \Nfreezes for the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My na... is... Fred... Prin... to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But so lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat's gone bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's frozen stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can feel the earnest \Nnervousness in her performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those Lamaze method actors, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... With ten swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She skipped forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nervous, she's barely breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With ten swords of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More, Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're risking your life \Njust watching this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's broken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to try whatever \Nwe can to cover for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my entrance yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please save me, Prince Frederick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:33.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been captured by Seinhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seinhart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:35.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Julius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the Princess back, then fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Seinhart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is really talented!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:53.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Erza's reached her limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Clock, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Horologium!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"F-Fight, fight!" she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if Frederick is defeated \Nhere, then the story can't progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Clock, how excellent of you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow Prince Frederick \Nto rest a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caught my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Sword of ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, y-you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have t-ten swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What realism!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call the marriage blues?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long until he appears?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Prince Frederick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess Yanderica, let us make many children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About 30 or so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that moving a bit fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait! I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Prince Frederick is dreamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This play is surreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brief respite is now over, thusly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Julius is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the "thusly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, my dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally my cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy everything! I am a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The red dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we must join forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... That's quite reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that called it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a twist is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, they're eloping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray's one smooth operator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice, ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hog the spotlight \Nwhen you suck so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:50.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Yanderica's awesome body is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing showing up on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always protect you \Nand your nice body, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he even show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case... I-I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...punish you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all gone to heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I have a really bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macky, hurry up and retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the curse of the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Frederick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, one week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it was such a huge hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for a bunch of stand-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give us our reward already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three performances a day is way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lazy bums! Hurry up and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want... I want to go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:24:01.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey Natsu! I think Llllloke \Ntotally lllllikes Lllllucy! {I know he doesn't say "like" but this helps the humor and matches the tongue rolling. My idea is it's like the "Ruffles have ridges" ad from my youth?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you role your tongue like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, Loke is always avoiding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just playing hard to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sure, whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.24,0:24:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Star that \NCannot Return to the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Llllloke totallllly lllllikes Lllllucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just feel like talking that way, don't you?
